{"tid":552870,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"消息指 獌聯 賤種蝗迷 明天提早放年假","createTime":"2018-02-07T03:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T04:45:03.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38c22a4b0a831f6a919f68bda11bf74c39e72310","tid":552870,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"【流感肆虐】消息指幼園小學明起停課防爆發 提早放年假<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞 2018-02-07 10:33:01 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冬季流感肆虐，逾百間學校爆發流感，特首林鄭月娥昨午與港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇，以及中大醫學院呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌會面，聽取有關疫苗注射成效、流感病理情況，並指會聽取專家意見後才可決定學校是否需要提早放農曆新年假，以減低感染情況，她強調要做決定前要有科學基礎。多間傳媒今早引述消息指，因應流感爆發嚴重，幼稚園和小學明天(本周四)起停課。"},{"pid":"9758e1df324dfd77a12a83f8be465d6a57209ec8","tid":552870,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"怪鳥王騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66228a6a2f7ff62a0246053f1b919bdf0d86aa17","tid":552870,"uid":57035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgcdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2016/11/02/14780950782167512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.kdnet.net%2FUploadSmall%2F2016%2F11%2F02%2F14780950782167512.jpg&h=a49e1cfe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72c41c7597af79b5a6074bb01002d9c9a1b8e8a9","tid":552870,"uid":33730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"樓主仲未柒夠呀, 炒車炒到甩轆喇<br />\n返去你個宇宙先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n高普賽後表示 球證有向他承認犯錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/550681/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/550681/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"0085cef644975942aa163340e2426b29a9ef7e19","tid":552870,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pi